@@TJvScrollBox.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes a new TJvScrollBox object.
Description
  Use \Create to create and initialize a new TJvScrollBox object.
  
  \Create calls the inherited \Create method, then sets the initial values for the scroll box as follows: 

  * HintColor is set to clInfoBk.
  * HotTrack is set to False.
  * csAcceptsControls is added to ControlStyle.  
Parameters
  AOwner - A component, typically the form, that is responsible for freeing the scroll box.
See Also
  HintColor, HotTrack
