@@TJvScrollBox.WndProc
Summary
  Responds to mouse clicks.
Description
  WndProc overrides the WndProc for TWinControl to respond when the user presses the left mouse button,
  while the mouse pointer is over the scroll box. If so, it sets focus to the scroll box.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the Windows message.
